"Setting up <Leader> key for easymotion
map <Leader> <Plug>(easymotion-prefix)

" Jump to anywhere you want with minimal keystrokes, with just one key
" binding. `s{char}{label}`
nmap s <Plug>(easymotion-overwin-f)

